From: mili Dev <dev@mili.local>
Date: Sat, 13 Jun 2026 16:30:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Pufferfish: Optimize mob spawning (Folia compatible)

Original license: GPL v3
Original project: https://github.com/pufferfish-gg/Pufferfish

This patch optimizes mob spawning by caching spawn state per-region.
Folia already has regionized mob spawning, so async threading is not needed.
This version caches the spawn state to avoid redundant calculations.

